snippet.title: Error Loop trailer
snippet.description: The ultimate troll game: It won't let you play, but it won't let you quit either. You're stuck forever in those endless menus full of glitches, unless you find a way to break the code open. A very unusual puzzle-game that will make you think outside the box.
